CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 13, 1957, pg. 13 reads: "Daisy E. Lampkin Lauded for Service to Mankind At Colorful Testimonial in Webster Hall - Distinguished Guests, all of whom were programmed, included, Mrs. Robert L. Vann, Roy Wilkins, Judge Homer S. Brown, the Rev. O.M. Walton and the Rev. Charles H. Foggie."
TitMainTitle: Jessie Vann, Roy Wilkins, Judge Homer S. Brown, Rev. O. M. Walton, and Rev. Charles H. Foggie, seated at banquet table in Webster Hall for honoree Daisy Lampkin
